race.comment: HOLLYWOOD NORTH (2) went close at Eagle Farm three back and then on the back of a disappointing run as favourite at the Sunshine Coast, delivered an easy Open win at Rockhampton. Hits this at peak fitness with a handy 3kg claim and rates to go on with the job. PRANCING WITH FIRE (8) has returned to racing in good order and followed a second at this track with a tidy win over 1400m at Casino. Fitter again, and she should be right in the finish. INTOXEL (7) was quickly back in the winners' stall, leading and winning at Grafton with a bit in reserve. Uses the rail and is sure to give a sight. BADGERS NUTS (1) presents off a win in Open grade at the Gold Coast. Has to carry 7.5kg more back to this level, but can't be ruled out.
